WORKFLOW-3.0
============

This directory contains the distribution for Workflow system, release 3.0, 
beta version. 


USING WORKFLOW
==============
*) Run 'deploy.sh' script, which should be under workflow installation area.
   This script prompts the user for the workflow deployment directory and 
   the worflow id generator class and modifies the installtion files 
   accordingly. 

*) Source 'exec_env.tcsh' script, which should be under the workflow 
   installation area.

*) Now, workflow tools should be ready to be used.


PROBLEMS
========
Please send any feedback to antware@tigr.org

Thanks for trying out the Workflow System.

